#: ../../../policy/CMP0001.rst:2
msgid "CMP0001"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/include/REMOVED_PROLOGUE.rst:2
msgid ""
"The ``OLD`` behavior of this policy was removed in CMake version |"
"REMOVED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION|. This policy must be set to ``NEW`` by a call to :"
"command:`cmake_minimum_required` or :command:`cmake_policy`."
msgstr ""
"該方針的 ``OLD`` 行為已在 CMake 版本 |REMOVED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION| 中移除。該方"
"針必須透過呼叫 :command:`cmake_minimum_required` 或 :command:`cmake_policy` "
"設定為 ``NEW``。"

#: ../../../policy/CMP0001.rst:7
msgid "``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` should no longer be used."
msgstr "``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` 不應再被使用。"

#: ../../../policy/CMP0001.rst:9
msgid ""
"The behavior is to check ``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` and present it to "
"the user.  The ``NEW`` behavior is to ignore "
"``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` completely."
msgstr ""
"此方針是檢查 ``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` 並呈現給使用者。``NEW`` 方針是"
"完全忽略 ``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY``。"

#: ../../../policy/CMP0001.rst:13
msgid ""
"In CMake 2.4 and below the variable ``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` was "
"used to request compatibility with earlier versions of CMake.  In CMake 2.6 "
"and above all compatibility issues are handled by policies and the :command:"
"`cmake_policy` command.  However, CMake must still check "
"``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` for projects written for CMake 2.4 and "
"below."
msgstr ""
"在 CMake 2.4 和更低版本中，變數 ``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY`` 用於請求與"
"早期版本的 CMake 相容。在 CMake 2.6 和更高版本中，所有相容性問題均由方針和 :"
"command:`cmake_policy` 命令處理。然而，對於為 CMake 2.4 和更低版本編寫的專"
"案，CMake 仍必須檢查 ``CMAKE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY``。"

#: ../../../policy/include/REMOVED_EPILOGUE.rst:1
msgid ""
"This policy was introduced in CMake version |INTRODUCED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION|. "
"Prior to removal in CMake version |REMOVED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION|, it could be "
"set by :command:`cmake_policy` or :command:`cmake_minimum_required`. If it "
"was not set, CMake |WARNED_OR_DID_NOT_WARN|, and used ``OLD`` behavior."
msgstr ""
"此方針於 CMake 版本 |INTRODUCED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION| 中引入。在 CMake 版本 |"
"REMOVED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION| 移除之前，它可以透過 :command:`cmake_policy` 或 :"
"command:`cmake_minimum_required` 設定。如果未設定，CMake |"
"WARNED_OR_DID_NOT_WARN|，並使用 ``OLD`` 行為。"
